    %% === DATA FLOWS ===

    %% Discovery → Engagement
    IG -->|DM| MC
    IG -->|Keyword comment/story| LAYLO
    WEB -->|Visit| STRIPE
    REF -->|Direct link| STRIPE

    %% ManyChat flows
    MC -->|Share Booking Link goal| CAL
    MC -->|Capture Email goal| NOTIFY

    %% Laylo → n8n
    LAYLO -->|"Webhook: email, phone, productId"| WF4
    WF4 -->|"Create lead record<br/>Status: Lead - Laylo"| PAYMENTS
    WF4 -->|Alert| NOTIFY

    %% Stripe → n8n
    STRIPE -->|"Webhook: checkout.session.completed<br/>name, email, phone, amount, session_id<br/>(line_items NOT included)"| WF1
    WF1 -->|"Create payment record<br/>Status: Paid - Needs Booking"| PAYMENTS
    WF1 -->|Subscribe contact| LAYLO
    WF1 -->|Send Calendly link| HELLO
    WF1 -->|Alert| NOTIFY

    %% Calendly → n8n
    CAL -->|"Webhook: invitee.created<br/>name, email, start_time, uri"| WF2
    WF2 -->|"Update status + call date<br/>Status: Booked - Needs Intake"| PAYMENTS
    WF2 -->|Alert| NOTIFY

    %% Tally → n8n
    TALLY -->|"Webhook: form submission<br/>all intake fields via data.fields array"| WF3
    WF3 -->|Create intake record| INTAKE
    WF3 -->|"POST /v1/messages<br/>intake text → analysis"| CLAUDE
    CLAUDE -->|"ai_summary + upsell_detected"| WF3
    WF3 -->|Update AI summary| INTAKE
    WF3 -->|"Link intake ↔ payment<br/>Status: Intake Complete"| PAYMENTS
    WF3 -->|Alert + upsell flag| NOTIFY

    %% Follow-ups
    WF5 -->|Query all records| PAYMENTS
    WF5 -->|Booking reminder| HELLO
    WF5 -->|Stale booking alert| NOTIFY

    WF6 -->|Query all records| PAYMENTS
    WF6 -->|"Intake reminder<br/>(Tally link: tally.so/r/b5W1JE)"| HELLO
    WF6 -->|Missing intake alert| NOTIFY

    WF7 -->|Query all records| PAYMENTS
    WF7 -->|Nurture email| HELLO
    WF7 -->|Lead nurture alert| NOTIFY

    %% Email → Team
    NOTIFY -->|All alerts| JAKE
    NOTIFY -->|All alerts| MEGHA
    NOTIFY -->|All alerts| SHARED

